<title>USA: Scopus Technology to make stock split.</title>
<headline>Scopus Technology to make stock split.</headline>
<dateline>EMERYVILLE, Calif. 1997-01-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Scopus Technology Inc said Wednesday it will conduct a three-for-two split of its common stock via a stock dividend.  </p>
<p>Scopus, which offers computer services, said it will pay the dividend by February 19 to stockholders of record on February 7.</p>
<p>The company has about 13.5 million shares in circulation.</p>
<p>It did not say how much its quarterly dividend was and company officials were not immediately available to comment.</p>
